source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Double-click an element

Usage: bl dblclick [OPTIONS] <selector>

Arguments:
  <selector>  CSS selector or @ref of the element to double-click

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl dblclick "td.cell"
  # Double-click to edit a table cell

  bl dblclick @e2
  # Double-click element from map
